tool_description: The AirVantage® M2M Cloud simplifies M2M development by providing a seamless connection between devices, the M2M cloud and the enterprise. - See more at: http://www.sierrawireless.com/en/productsandservices/AirVantage_M2M_Cloud/How_It_Works.aspx
name: AirVantage M2M Cloud
title: AirVantage M2M Cloud

api_list.name: Activate
api_list.description: Activate systems from label or from a list of UID.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://dsciamma-airvantage-m2m-cloud.p.rapidapi.com/operations/systems/activate"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "dsciamma-airvantage-m2m-cloud.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
